asus.com.cn/websites/global/images/icons/vga/gputweak_big.png\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; display: block; max-width: none;\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td height=\"250\"><img class=\"center\" border=\"0\" alt=\"2GB GDDR5 Memory\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/CN/products/s9Y8aKi3qSkuimNM/image007.jpg\" longdesc=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/Graphics_Cards/GTX760DC2OC4GD5/\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; display: block; max-width: none;\" /></td>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h5 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.8em; font-family: inherit; line-height: 13.920000076293945px; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 14px;\">4GB GDDR5超大显存</h5>\r\n            4GB超大显存满足大屏与高分辨率显示需求！</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"columns\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px;\">\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.8em; font-weight: bolder; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 16px; background-image: url(http://www.asus.com.cn/images/h4_bg.gif); height: auto; padding: 6px 5px 7px 20px; background-attachment: scroll; border-top-left-radius: 5px; border-top-right-radius: 5px; border-bottom-right-radius: 5px; border-bottom-left-radius: 5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat no-repeat;\">华硕显卡特性</h4>\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"20\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background-color: transparent; border-spacing: 20px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" width=\"8%\"><img alt=\"NVIDIA GeForce\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/images/icons/vga/nvidiageforcegtx.png\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; max-width: none;\" /></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" width=\"41%\">\r\n            <h5 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.8em; font-family: inherit; line-height: 13.920000076293945px; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 14px;\">采用GeForce&reg; GTX 760</h5>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" width=\"8%\"><img alt=\"NVIDIA&reg; GPU Boost\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/images/icons/vga/gpuboost.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; max-width: none;\" /></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" width=\"41%\">\r\n            <h5 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.8em; font-family: inherit; line-height: 13.920000076293945px; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 14px;\">NVIDIA&reg; GPU Boost 2.0</h5>\r\n            通过 NVIDIA GPU Boost技术，展现 GeForce GTX 显卡全新层级的卓越性能。该技术可动态调整频率速度极大化，以提供每一场游戏的最佳性能。</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\"><img alt=\"Adaptive Vertical Sync\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/images/icons/vga/adaptivev-sync.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; max-width: none;\" /></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\">\r\n            <h5 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.8em; font-family: inherit; line-height: 13.920000076293945px; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 14px;\">NVIDIA&reg; Adaptive V-Sync</h5>\r\n            通过 NVIDIA Adaptive Vertical Sync 游戏创新技术，不仅可获致更快的帧率，亦可获致更为流畅的游戏画面。这项技术可动态垂直同步调整到目前帧率，以呈现最佳的游戏性能。</td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\"><img alt=\"PhysX by NVIDIA\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/images/icons/vga/physxbynvidia.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; max-width: none;\" /></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\">\r\n            <h5 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.8em; font-family: inherit; line-height: 13.920000076293945px; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 14px;\">NVIDIA&reg; PhysX&trade;</h5>\r\n            通过先进的特效，尽情享受游戏体验，例如例如燃烧爆炸，反应碎片，真实的水效果及栩栩如生的人物，以10倍的速度在图形处理和物理运算之间快速切换，从而使更复杂的效果得以实时呈现。</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\"><img alt=\"NVIDIA SLI Ready\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/images/icons/vga/nvidiasliready.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; max-width: none;\" /></td>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h5 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.8em; font-family: inherit; line-height: 13.920000076293945px; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 14px;\">支持SLI</h5>\r\n            多重图形显示技术，提供极致的性能。</td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\"><img alt=\"NVIDIA 3D Vision Ready\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/images/icons/vga/nvidia3dvisionready.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; max-width: none;\" /></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\">\r\n            <h5 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.8em; font-family: inherit; line-height: 13.920000076293945px; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 14px;\">支持NVIDIA&reg; 3D Vision&trade; Surround技术</h5>\r\n            可将数百种PC游戏转换成真正立体3D视觉体验，并可跨越三部显示器，在令人赞叹的 5760x1080 分辨率下，享受身历其境的 full HD 3D 效果。</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\"><img alt=\"PCIE 3.0\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/images/icons/vga/pcie302xdatabandwidth.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; max-width: none;\" /></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\">\r\n            <h5 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.8em; font-family: inherit; line-height: 13.920000076293945px; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 14px;\">支持PCIE3.0</h5>\r\n            相较于上一代的PCIE2.0规格，PCIE3.0的带宽提升了两倍，使 GPU&mdash;CPU的传输速率更快。</td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"Full DirectX 11.1 API support\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/images/icons/vga/dx11.1lifelikegraphics.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; max-width: none;\" /></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\">\r\n            <h5 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.8em; font-family: inherit; line-height: 13.920000076293945px; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 14px;\">支持Microsoft DirectX 11.1 API (feature level 11_0)</h5>\r\n            让用户在计算机上尽情享受栩栩如生的游戏体验，并获得更佳的效能。</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\"><img alt=\"PCIE 3.0\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/images/icons/vga/windows8compatible.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; max-width: none;\" /></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\">\r\n            <h5 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.8em; font-family: inherit; line-height: 13.920000076293945px; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 14px;\">兼容Microsoft&reg; Windows&reg; 8</h5>\r\n            让您通过最新的操作系统，使用高级运算的体验，因此，您可利用 PC 做更多的事情。</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>','images/201402/thumb_img/6758_thumb_G_1393264968006.jpg','images/201402/goods_img/6758_G_1393264968593.jpg','images/201402/source_img/6758_G_1393264968575.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1393264968','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1398369254','5','','2','0','0','0');
