;</td>\r\n                        <td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n                        <td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cn.msi.com/pic/image/feature/mb/cbios_5.png\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\"feature-list\" style=\"background-image: url(http://cn.msi.com/images/front/line.gif); background-position: 50% 100%; background-repeat: repeat no-repeat;\">\r\n            <td class=\"new-ftbox\" width=\"150\" height=\"200\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px 0px 0px; min-width: 150px; background-image: url(http://cn.msi.com/images/front/feature_line_h.jpg); min-height: 200px; background-position: 100% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><img src=\"http://cn.msi.com/pic/feature/feature_20130517133414.png\" alt=\"featurePic\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></td>\r\n            <td class=\"new-ftboxl\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 3px 1em;\">\r\n            <h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 15px;\">USB 3.0</h3>\r\n            <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">与 USB 2.0 的 480Mbps 速度相比，USB 3.0 的 5Gb/s 提供了十倍的传输带宽。让你传输一片蓝光电影仅需要不到一分钟的时间。<br />\r\n            <br />\r\n            <strong>特色</strong><br />\r\n            - 革命性超快速 USB 3.0, 比 USB 2.0 快 10 倍<br />\r\n            - 让 PC 与 USB 装置之间享有高达 5Gbps 带宽, 大幅提升数据传输率</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\"feature-list\" style=\"background-image: url(http://cn.msi.com/images/front/line.gif); background-position: 50% 100%; background-repeat: repeat no-repeat;\">\r\n            <td class=\"new-ftbox\" width=\"150\" height=\"200\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px 0px 0px; min-width: 150px; background-image: url(http://cn.msi.com/images/front/feature_line_h.jpg); min-height: 200px; background-position: 100% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><img src=\"http://cn.msi.com/pic/feature/feature_20130517133456.png\" alt=\"featurePic\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></td>\r\n            <td class=\"new-ftboxl\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 3px 1em;\">\r\n            <h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 15px;\">SATA 6Gb/s</h3>\r\n            <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">SATA 6Gb/s 提供比传统 SATA 3Gb/s 高两倍的带宽，让主板与内部储存装置如7200转的硬盘、10000RPM的硬盘和固态硬盘的数据传输更快速。也为即将到来的高速内部存储设备，打破电脑的性能瓶颈，也是目前最主流的接口配置。<br />\r\n            <br />\r\n            <strong>特色</strong><br />\r\n            - 支持下一代 SATAIII, 高达 6Gbps 带宽<br />\r\n            - 数据传输率比 SATAII (3Gbps) 高一倍</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\"feature-list\" style=\"background-image: url(http://cn.msi.com/images/front/line.gif); background-position: 50% 100%; background-repeat: repeat no-repeat;\">\r\n            <td class=\"new-ftbox\" width=\"150\" height=\"200\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px 0px 0px; min-width: 150px; background-image: url(http://cn.msi.com/images/front/feature_line_h.jpg); min-height: 200px; background-position: 100% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><img src=\"http://cn.msi.com/pic/feature/feature_20130806095610.jpg\" alt=\"featurePic\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></td>\r\n            <td class=\"new-ftboxl\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 3px 1em;\">\r\n            <h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 15px;\">Intel&reg; Smart Connect</h3>\r\n            <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">- 全自动更新及同步处理电子邮件、社群网站内容、新闻以及其他数据<br />\r\n            - 即使系统处于休眠模式，也会定期唤醒并更新已开启的应用程序</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\"feature-list\" style=\"background-image: url(http://cn.msi.com/images/front/line.gif); background-position: 50% 100%; background-repeat: repeat no-repeat;\">\r\n            <td class=\"new-ftbox\" width=\"150\" height=\"200\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px 0px 0px; min-width: 150px; background-image: url(http://cn.msi.com/images/front/feature_line_h.jpg); min-height: 200px; background-position: 100% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><img src=\"http://cn.msi.com/pic/feature/feature_20130517105752.png\" alt=\"featurePic\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></td>\r\n            <td class=\"new-ftboxl\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 3px 1em;\">\r\n            <h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 15px;\">Live Update 5</h3>\r\n            <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cn.msi.com/pic/image/product_img/other/mainboard/feature/live_200.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 5px 10px; width: 200px; float: right; height: 147px;\" />Live Update&trade; 5 是一套具备强大功能且方便使用的应用程序，可自动检测、实时更新系统装置的驱动程序及BIOS，藉此可省下搜寻各种驱动程序及BIOS的时间与降低风险。<br />\r\n            <br />\r\n            <strong>特色</strong><br />\r\n            - 自动侦测 BIOS/驱动程序/显卡/工具软件更新<br />\r\n            - 支持微软 Windows XP/Vista/7 32/64 位</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\"feature-list\" style=\"background-image: url(http://cn.msi.com/images/front/line.gif); background-position: 50% 100%; background-repeat: repeat no-repeat;\">\r\n            <td class=\"new-ftbox\" width=\"150\" height=\"200\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px 0px 0px; min-width: 150px; background-image: url(http://cn.msi.com/images/front/feature_line_h.jpg); min-height: 200px; background-position: 100% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><img src=\"http://cn.msi.com/pic/feature/feature_20130517105800.png\" alt=\"featurePic\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></td>\r\n            <td class=\"new-ftboxl\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 3px 1em;\">\r\n            <h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 15px;\">M-Flash</h3>\r\n            <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">相比传统主板需要大容量的BIOS芯片，微星的M-Flash有一个双重的优势，其一是他不需要额外的组件支持；其二是他能将你的bios数据保存在USB移动设备中。保存下的数据不只具有备份和升级功能，同时它还可被视为一个便携式的bios，可以帮你重新启动你的电脑。<br />\r\n            <br />\r\n            <strong>特色</strong><br />\r\n            - 速度快，灵活性高。<br />\r\n            - 当BIOS损毁时可由USB随身碟载入BIOS档案进行开机修复作业。<br />\r\n            - 可从BIOS内利用M-Flash功能，从USB随身碟内载入BIOS更新档进行更新作业。</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\"feature-list\" style=\"background-image: url(http://cn.msi.com/images/front/line.gif); background-position: 50% 100%; background-repeat: repeat no-repeat;\">\r\n            <td class=\"new-ftbox\" width=\"150\" height=\"200\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px 0px 0px; min-width: 150px; background-image: url(http://cn.msi.com/images/front/feature_line_h.jpg); min-height: 200px; background-position: 100% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><img src=\"http://cn.msi.com/pic/feature/feature_20130517171317.png\" alt=\"featurePic\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></td>\r\n            <td class=\"new-ftboxl\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 3px 1em;\">\r\n            <h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 15px;\">Click BIOS 4</h3>\r\n            <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; height: 18px; width: 725px;\">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">微星 Click BIOS 4 是专