c=\"http://cn.msi.com/pic/image/feature/mb/cbios_2.png\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 230px; height: 173px;\" /></p>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n                        <td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Board Explorer</strong></span><br />\r\n                        <br />\r\n                        <img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cn.msi.com/pic/image/feature/mb/cbios_3.png\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 230px; height: 173px;\" /></td>\r\n                        <td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n                        <td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>OC Profile Preview</strong></span><br />\r\n                        <br />\r\n                        <img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cn.msi.com/pic/image/feature/mb/cbios_4.png\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 230px; height: 173px;\" /></td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;<br />\r\n                        Hardware Monitor 可让你透过 Total Fan 控制系统，并以图形接口检查系统的各项数据。</td>\r\n                        <td valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n                        <td valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br />\r\n                        Board Explorer 可利用鼠标来检查主板组件的详细信息，快速辨识连接的接端口与装置。<br />\r\n                        <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">*真实效能与图片可能因主板不同而有所差异。</span></td>\r\n                        <td valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n                        <td valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br />\r\n                        提供八个数据文件设定存盘，让你可以快速了解目前系统设定与其他设定的区别。</td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </td>\r\n  